item.title: Christina Applegate: Survival of the Funniest
item.description: Christina Applegate has always had a dark sense of humor. And she leans on it big time to deal with a series of enormous obstacles and challenges. As a child star-turned-household name (thanks to 11 seasons on “Married...with Children”) Christina avoids the pitfalls of other kid actors and becomes one of Hollywood’s leading ladies of comedy... item.title: Imran Khan vs Shahbaz Sharif, Dr. Mahrang Arrested, Rajab Butt Flees, Kunal Kamra Silenced? TWIP
item.description: In today's episode we discuss the arrests of Dr. Mahrang Baloch, Sami Deen Baloch, Waheed Murad, Pakistan being a hard state, Imran Khan vs Shahbaz Sharif, Rajab Butt fleeing Pakistan, Kunal Kamra being silenced in India and US bill seeking sanctions on Pakistan.Uzair Younus and Shehzad Ghias do the round up of this week's news in our new show 'This Week in Pakistan.
